(51572, 81281, 0, 1, 'Who are you', '一段APP的感情，未知也無結局', '2012-07-18 00:00:00', 2000, 15, 0, 14, 'The clock goes ticking,\r\nAnd I am waiting for the words to come to me,\r\nStaring at the screen\r\n\r\nYour dreams and visions,\r\nYour hope for life and expectations speak to me,\r\nPull me to the screen\r\n\r\nAnd we''re both waiting,\r\nLet me come to you.\r\n\r\nWho are you?\r\nWho are you?\r\nWho are you?\r\n\r\nMy heart''s sinking,\r\nIn the darkness with this veil you''ve put on me,\r\nI cannot see.\r\n\r\nMy heart beats not quite right,\r\nErratic like the cold waves that now pour on me,\r\nI go back to that screen.\r\n\r\nAnd we''re both waiting,\r\nLet me come to you.\r\n', '', 142, '', 'NiC Lee', 'Nic Lee', 'NiC', 'I Do Music', '', 0, 1, 0, '2012-07-18 16:19:53', '2015-03-12 13:54:26', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
